c: 46
v: 20
t: "Ne inyanga yabakhayi balirerwa mumulilo, baliboolelwa mbu: “mwamala okhubukula ebilayi bienyu khubulamu bwokhushialo, mana nimubwikhoyela, kho lelo luno murungwa eshinyasio shietsisoni khulwa okhufura khwenyu khushialo khunjila ilali yatoto, Nende khulwa amabii kenyu kamwakholanga.”"